                     <interp inst="t18270913-108-person1170" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I heard the cry of Stop thief! and saw the prisoner running across the road - he made his way towards Goulston-street - he was brought back, and I took hold of him; Copping came up, and said, "That is the man that took my watch;" the prisoner had no watch then, but Copping said he had taken the watch from him before - that he got from him again, and I took him.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I heard the cry of Stop thief! and this man came and took me - Copping said I was the man, but I never saw the watch.</p>
